title: Lucky Twice - Young & Clever 2007
description:
Lucky Twice - Young & Clever 2007
Mp3 320 mbit/s

Lucky Twice is a Swedish teenage pop duo consisting of seventeen year old Hannah Reynold and seventeen year old Emelie Schytz. They are signed to Family Tree Music in Sweden. Victoria Ekeberg is their manager who has a hugh succes with September, Gathania & Nexx.

Their first single "Lucky", was released in Spain on July 20, 2006 through Vale Music. It went to number 1 in the singles chart and was certified double platinum. Their album Young & Clever was released in June 2007 and was followed on July 23 by the single "Hop Non Stop".
